@page "/"

<PageTitle>Style Manager App</PageTitle>

<div class="text-center mt-5">
    <h1 class="display-4">👕 Style Manager</h1>
    <p class="lead">Welcome to the Style Manager Application — built with <strong>Blazor Server</strong> and <strong>.NET 8</strong>.</p>

    <p>This app allows you to:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>✅ Add and manage <strong>Colors</strong></li>
        <li>✅ Add and manage <strong>Sizes</strong></li>
        <li>✅ Create <strong>Styles</strong> by combining color, size, and a style number</li>
        <li>✅ View all created styles in a clean list</li>
    </ul>

    <p>You can use the navigation bar on the left to start adding or viewing styles.</p>

    <hr />

    <p class="text-muted">Made with ❤️ by Adnan</p>
</div>
